short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Leetcoach adds a chat window to Leetcode, allowing you to discuss your problem with chatGPT.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Leetcoach allows you to easily get feedback on your work by talking to a ChatGPT session that automatically knows the problem and your current solution. The chat window is added in the bottom right with seamless UI that allows you to use the chat as much or as little as you want.

To use Leetcoach, just install the extension, and open up a Leetcode problem as you normally would.
